          <h2>Two Platforms, One Goal</h2>
          <p class="guide-section__intro">BharatNotes and Ujiyari are built to work as a system. BharatNotes gives you the static backbone — syllabus-aligned notes, NCERT summaries, PYQs, and practice tools. Ujiyari gives you the live layer — daily news, editorial analysis, and current affairs mapped to the same UPSC syllabus. Together they cover everything an aspirant needs from Day 1 to Interview.</p>

